trans-unit.source: Represents the dynamic delete index operation at the call site, providing the binding semantic and the details about the operation.
trans-unit.target: 代表呼叫位置上的動態刪除索引作業，並提供繫結語意和作業的詳細資料。

trans-unit.source: The signature of the arguments at the call site.
trans-unit.target: 位於呼叫位置的引數簽章。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Dynamic.DeleteIndexBinder" />.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:System.Dynamic.DeleteIndexBinder" /> 的新執行個體。

trans-unit.source: The target of the dynamic delete index operation.
trans-unit.target: 動態刪除索引作業的目標。

trans-unit.source: An array of arguments of the dynamic delete index operation.
trans-unit.target: 動態刪除索引作業的引數陣列。

trans-unit.source: Performs the binding of the dynamic delete index operation.
trans-unit.target: 執行動態刪除索引作業的繫結。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Dynamic.DynamicMetaObject" /> representing the result of the binding.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Dynamic.DynamicMetaObject" />，表示繫結結果。

trans-unit.source: Gets the signature of the arguments at the call site.
trans-unit.target: 取得位於呼叫位置的引數簽章。

trans-unit.source: The signature of the arguments at the call site.
trans-unit.target: 位於呼叫位置的引數簽章。

trans-unit.source: Performs the binding of the dynamic delete index operation if the target dynamic object cannot bind.
trans-unit.target: 如果目標動態物件無法繫結，則會執行動態刪除索引作業的繫結。

trans-unit.source: The target of the dynamic delete index operation.
trans-unit.target: 動態刪除索引作業的目標。

trans-unit.source: The arguments of the dynamic delete index operation.
trans-unit.target: 動態刪除索引作業的引數。

trans-unit.source: Performs the binding of the dynamic delete index operation if the target dynamic object cannot bind.
trans-unit.target: 如果目標動態物件無法繫結，則會執行動態刪除索引作業的繫結。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Dynamic.DynamicMetaObject" /> representing the result of the binding.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Dynamic.DynamicMetaObject" />，表示繫結結果。

trans-unit.source: The target of the dynamic delete index operation.
trans-unit.target: 動態刪除索引作業的目標。

trans-unit.source: The arguments of the dynamic delete index operation.
trans-unit.target: 動態刪除索引作業的引數。

trans-unit.source: The binding result to use if binding fails, or null.
trans-unit.target: 繫結失敗時要使用的繫結結果或 null。

trans-unit.source: When overridden in the derived class, performs the binding of the dynamic delete index operation if the target dynamic object cannot bind.
trans-unit.target: 在衍生類別中覆寫時，如果目標動態物件無法繫結，則會執行動態刪除索引作業的繫結。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Dynamic.DynamicMetaObject" /> representing the result of the binding.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Dynamic.DynamicMetaObject" />，表示繫結結果。

trans-unit.source: The result type of the operation.
trans-unit.target: 運算的結果類型。

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Type" /> object representing the result type of the operation.
trans-unit.target: 表示作業之結果類型的 <see cref="T:System.Type" /> 物件。
